column5: I am looking for a partner to fish with in my boat on the upper for skis tomorow. I want to leave casablanca by 6:30 and be back by 5:00.... interested pm me and i will get back to you as soon as i can. Pat
Hey Pat, it'll be good to see you on the river tomorrow, it's been a long time since Quinte
Yeah remember the first time we met i was in rough shape....
Yeah, but things were lots better the 2nd time
Yeah the fish were not biting but the company was great. ttys Pay
hope someone jumps in on this invite Pat.
HMMMM.. nope, better not, my luck I'd rip the stitches out of my neck hoistin the big gal! LOL  Where's slowpoke on this one. BRIAN !!!!
bump...see you at the marina in the morning.  Funny, I'm leaving from Casablanca too, maybe see you on the road
